column1: PAL1314_LMG1401_particulate_pos_withoddFA.csv, lipids identified in particulate (0.2 um) samples from Arthur Harbor and along PAL-LTER cruise grid, 2014-2014 (PAL1314 and LMG1401)
Identifications were made by J. Collins, james.r.collins@aya.yale.edu, using v1.1.1 of the LOBSTAHS lipidomics software package for R

Values in columns 13-17 of this speadsheet are raw chromatographic peak areas; the .xlsx file PAL1314_LMG1401_particulate_IP-DAG_pmol_mL.xlsx contains mass data for unoxidized IP-DAG obtained using authentic standards
